(6000035,'AWS_Autoscaling','<div class=\"AWS_Autoscaling\">\n    <h1>AWS Autoscaling</h1>\n    <h2 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Introduction:</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">AWS Auto Scaling, the solution that takes the\n                    complexity out of\n                    managing your AWS resources.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Say goodbye to manual scaling and hello to\n                    automatic adjustments that\n                    ensure your applications maintain optimal performance while optimizing\n                    costs.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">With AWS Auto Scaling, your infrastructure\n                    dynamically adapts to\n                    changing workloads, providing a seamless experience for your\n                    users.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Key Features and\n                        Benefits:</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Automated Resource\n                        Management:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">AWS Auto Scaling monitors your applications and\n                    automatically adjusts\n                    the capacity of your resources based on demand.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">This ensures that you have the right amount of\n                    resources available at\n                    all times, avoiding over-provisioning and unnecessary costs.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Maintain High\n                        Availability:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">With auto scaling, your applications are\n                    distributed across multiple\n                    instances.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">If\n                    one instance becomes unavailable, the others continue to serve\n                    traffic, maintaining high availability and reducing the risk of\n                    downtime.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Cost\n                        Optimization:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Pay for only the resources you need. Auto\n                    Scaling scales in during\n                    periods of lower demand, reducing costs, and scales out during peak\n                    times to handle increased traffic efficiently.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Easy\n                        Configuration:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Setting up Auto Scaling is straightforward,\n                    thanks to the\n                    user-friendly </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>AWS Management\n                            Console</strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">\n                    and </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>powerful\n                            APIs.&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Define scaling policies based on metrics such as\n                </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>CPUutilization, request\n                            count</strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">, or\n                </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>custom\n                            metrics</strong></span></strong><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Integration with Other AWS\n                        Services:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">AWS Auto Scaling seamlessly integrates with\n                    other AWS services, such\n                    as </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Elastic Load\n                            Balancing</strong></span></strong><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">, </span><strong\n                    style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Amazon\n                            EC2</strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">, and\n                </span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Amazon\n                            ECS</strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">, to\n                    provide a comprehensive and efficient solution for managing your\n                    applications.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>How AWS Auto Scaling\n                        Works:</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Create Scaling\n                        Plans:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Define your scaling requirements by configuring\n                    minimum and maximum\n                    resource limits, desired capacities, and scaling policies.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Monitoring and\n                        Metrics:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>AWS Auto\n                            Scaling</strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">\n                    continuously monitors the metrics you\'ve set to trigger scaling\n                    events.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">These metrics can include </span><strong\n                    style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>CPU\n                            utilization</strong></span></strong><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">, </span><strong\n                    style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                        style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>request\n                            counts</strong></span></strong><span style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">,\n                    and custom application metrics.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Scale Out and\n                        In:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Based on the scaling policies and thresholds\n                    you\'ve set, Auto Scaling\n                    will automatically add or remove resources as demand\n                    changes.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Scale out to handle increased traffic and scale\n                    in during periods of\n                    lower demand.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Use\n                        Cases:</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h2>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Web\n                        Applications:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Ensure your web applications can handle traffic\n                    spikes and sudden\n                    increases in user demand, providing a smooth experience for\n                    users.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Streaming and Media\n                        Services:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Automatically adjust resources to accommodate\n                    varying viewership\n                    levels and maintain an uninterrupted streaming experience.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>E-Commerce:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Meet the demands of high-traffic shopping events\n                    and seasonal\n                    fluctuations while optimizing costs during quieter periods.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Batch Processing\n                        Workloads:&nbsp;</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Scale resources up to handle heavy computational\n                    workloads and scale\n                    down during idle periods to save on costs.</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h3 class=\"MsoNormal\">\n        <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\"><strong>Conclusion:</strong></span></strong></span>\n    </h3>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc\">\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">AWS Auto Scaling empowers you to build resilient\n                    and cost-efficient\n                    applications by automatically adjusting your resources to match\n                    real-time demand.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n        <li style=\"list-style-type: disc; text-align: justify\">\n            <span style=\"font-family: \'Nunito Sans\', serif\"><span\n                    style=\"line-height: 107%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11pt\">Eliminate the need for manual intervention and\n                    experience the\n                    benefits of seamless scaling, high availability, and cost\n                    optimization.&nbsp;</span></span>\n        </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify\">&nbsp;</p>\n    <div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9\">\n        <iframe class=\"embed-responsive-item\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/909994753\" allowfullscreen=\"\"\n            allow=\"fullscreen\" data-ready=\"true\"></iframe>\n    </div>\n\n    <form method=\"post\">\n        <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"score\" name=\"score\" value=\"0\" />\n        <input type=\"hidden\" id=\"t_score\" name=\"t_score\" value=\"0\" />\n        <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"order\" value=\"38\" />\n        <button class=\"btn btn-block button-default design-sprint__item__button\" type=\"submit\" name=\"complete\">\n            COMPLETE\n        </button>\n    </form>\n</div>','2025-01-03 17:07:48'),
